'''Eko Purjianto''' (born on February 1, 1976) is an [[Indonesia]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who previously played as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[PSPS Pekanbaru]] and the [[Indonesia national football team|Indonesia national team]].<ref>{{NFT player|pid=24577}}</ref>

