==International career==
In 1999 Eko's international career began. He finished his international career on 27 May 2001 against [[China national football team|China]] in the [[2002 FIFA World Cup qualification]].<ref>[http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=4395/preliminaries/preliminary=3847/matches/match=20952/report.html Preliminary matches : Indonesia-China]</ref>

